sentences: Billy Joe Walker Jr. (February 29, 1952 – July 25, 2017) was an American songwriter, record producer and recording artist.
Between 1987 and 1994, he recorded seven solo albums, all for major labels.
Walker died following a period of declining health on July 25, 2017.
